husband%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.acterra.org%2Fblog%2F2023%2F7%2F25%2Fall-electric-road-trip%5C%22%3Eblog%20post%20on%20Acterra%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20environmental%20education%20nonprofit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20remote%20and%20almost%20entirely%20undeveloped%20%E2%80%93%20the%20perfect%20challenge%20for%20planning%20our%20first%20road%20trip%20in%20our%20new%2C%20all-electric%20Tesla%20Model%20Y%2C%26quot%3B%20Goforth%20wrote%20regarding%20the%20Carrizo%20Plain%2C%20a%20grassland%20in%20San%20Luis%20Obispo%20County%2C%20California%20that%20is%20about%2050%20miles%20long%20and%2015%20miles%20wide.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20no%20services%20within%20or%20anywhere%20near%20the%20Monument%20%E2%80%93%20no%20food%2C%20water%2C%20gas%20stations%2C%20and%2C%20certainly%2C%20no%20EV%20charging%20stations.%20Could%20we%20do%20it%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Tesla%20owner%20said%20she%20planned%20her%20route%20ahead%20of%20time%20using%20a%20Travelocity%20filter%20that%20allowed%20her%20to%20find%20hotels%20with%20EV%20chargers%2C%20as%20well%20as%20using%20Plugshare's%20Trip%20Planner%2C%20which%20helped%20her%20plot%20out%20the%20various%20charging%20stations%20along%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20greatest%20hurdle%20the%20couple%20faced%20during%20their%20trip%20was%20once%20they%20reached%20the%20Carrizo%20Plain%2C%20Goforth%20said%2C%20as%20there%20were%20no%20chargers%20within%20at%20least%2050%20miles%20of%20the%20location.%20At%20their%20first%20stop%2C%20the%20couple%20was%20able%20to%20make%20use%20of%20a%20Level%202%20fast%20charger%2C%20but%20they%20had%20to%20find%20different%20methods%20to%20charge%20at%20the%20California%20Valley%20Lodge%2C%20a%20motel%20just%2020%20miles%20outside%20of%20the%20Carrizo%20Plain%20National%20Monument.%20Goforth%20said%20the%20couple%20had%20initially%20planned%20to%20charge%20using%20an%20RV%20hook-up%20site%20near%20the%20lodge%20and%20they%20were%20a%20%26quot%3Blittle%20nervous%26quo