esting%20against%20the%20Ashok%20Gehlot-led%20Rajasthan%20government%20on%20a%20host%20of%20issues%20-%20including%20exam%20paper%20leaks%2C%20crimes%20against%20women%20and%20corruption%20-%20months%20ahead%20of%20Assembly%20elections%20in%20the%20state.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHundreds%20of%20BJP%20workers%2C%20who%20were%20marching%20towards%20the%20secretariat%20this%20afternoon%2C%20began%20dragging%20and%20removing%20barricades%2C%20leading%20to%20minor%20skirmishes%20with%20the%20police.%20A%20police%20official%20said%20water%20cannons%20had%20to%20be%20used%20against%20the%20protesters%20as%20they%20persisted%20in%20removing%20the%20barricades%20despite%20personnel%20trying%20to%20stop%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20march%2C%20which%20was%20organised%20as%20part%20of%20the%20opposition%20party's%20%26quot%3BNahi%20Sahega%20Rajasthan%26quot%3B%20campaign%2C%20saw%20workers%20participating%20from%20several%20districts%20of%20the%20state.%20The%20BJP%20had%20set%20a%20target%20of%201%20lakh%20workers%20and%20planned%20to%20surround%20the%20secretariat%2C%20but%20there%20was%20adequate%20deployment%20of%20police%20personnel%20as%20well%2C%20which%20prevented%20them%20from%20reaching%20the%20seat%20of%20power.%20Several%20senior%20BJP%20leaders%20were%20detained%20and%20then%20let%20off.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protest%20was%20against%20exam%20paper%20leaks%2C%20crimes%20against%20women%2C%20farmers'%20debts%20and%20distress%2C%20and%20corruption.%20One%20of%20the%20issues%20was%20also%20the%20red%20diary%20that%20had%20been%20waved%20by%20sacked%20minister%20Rajendra%20Singh%20Gudha%20in%20the%20Assembly%20last%20week.%20The%20former%20minister%20had%20claimed%20that%20the%20diary%20contains%20details%20of%20pay-offs%20made%20by%20the%20Gehlot%20camp%20to%20MLAs%20to%20save%20his%20government%20during%20the%202020%20rebellion%20led%20by%20Sachin%20Pilot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20march%20began%2C%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20Rajendra%20Rathore%20addressed%20the%20gathering%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BEvery%20worker%20of%20the%20party%20will%20work%20towards%20putting%20the%20final%20nail%20in%20the%20coffin%20of%20the%20Gehlot%20government.%20The%20people%20of%20Rajasthan%20will%20work%20towards%20opening%20the%20bandages%20on%20Mr%20Gehlot's%20legs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20sources%20said%20the%20party%20will%20now%20embark%20on%20a%20'Parivartan%20Yatra'%2C%20in%20which%20senior%20party%20leaders%20will%20visit%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20state.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20added%20that%2C%20in%20keeping%20with%20the%20formula%20of%20collective%20leadership%20that%20the%20party%20has%20worked%20out%20for%20the%20Assembly%20polls%2C%20the%20campaign%20will%20be%20helmed%20by%20former%20chief%20minister%20Vasundhara%20Raje%2C%20state%20BJP%20President%20CP%20Joshi%2C%20former%20state%20president%20Satish%20Poonia%2C%20Union%20Minister%20Gajendra%20Singh%20Shekhawat%20and%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20Rajendra%20Rathore.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690895940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2Fo28cv928_bjp-rajasthan-protest-water-cannons-650_625x300_01_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-workers-try-to-surround-rajasthan-secretariat-cops-use-water-cannons-4259548%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20police%20used%20water%20cannons%20against%20protesting%20BJP%20workers%20to%20prevent%20them%20from%20surrounding%20the%20government%20secretariat%20in%20Jaipur%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-workers-try-to-surround-rajasthan-secretariat-cops-use-water-cannons-4259548%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-workers-try-to-surround-rajasthan-secretariat-cops-use-water-cannons-4259548%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3