20Article%20370%20in%202019%2C%20was%20barred%20from%20leaving%20Kashmir%20and%20joining%20a%20leadership%20programme%20at%20the%20Yale%20University%20earlier%20this%20year%20by%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20that%20some%20journalists%20were%20also%20called%20up%20for%20questioning%20by%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%E2%80%99s%20counter-intelligence%20unit%20in%20Srinagar%20recently.%20At%20least%20four%20journalists%2C%20who%20spoke%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20on%20the%20condition%20of%20anonymity%2C%20said%20that%20the%20investigators%20asked%20them%20about%20a%20%E2%80%98Chinese%20journalist%E2%80%99%20who%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20visited%20Kashmir%20recently%20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20asked%20whether%20I%20met%20this%20Chinese%20journalist%20but%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20what%20they%20were%20talking%20about%2C%20and%20I%20told%20them%20so%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20one%20of%20the%20journalists%2C%20wishing%20to%20remain%20anonymous.%20He%20said%20that%20the%20investigators%20ran%20him%20through%20a%20questionnaire%20comprising%20dozens%20of%20%E2%80%9Cpersonal%20and%20professional%E2%80%9D%20questions%2C%20including%20details%20of%20bank%20payments%20and%20travel%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAn%20ongoing%20process%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20authorities%20have%20imposed%20restrictions%20on%20the%20movement%20of%20some%20Kashmiri%20activists%20and%20journalists%2C%20who%20work%20with%20national%20and%20international%20organisations.%20Free%20speech%20activists%20have%20alleged%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Ccriminalisation%20of%20journalism%E2%80%9D%20is%20part%20of%20a%20wider%20crackdown%20on%20free%20speech%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20which%20directly%20runs%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20Sanna%20Irshad%20Mattoo%2C%2029%2C%20a%20Srinagar-based%20photojournalist%20and%20a%20Magnum%20Foundation%20fel