0Cooke%2C%20so%20it's%20time%20to%20start%20planning.%20Here's%20what%20to%20expect%20and%20how%20to%20see%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20stars%20are%20aligned%20for%20a%20good%20show%20this%20year%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Perseids%20are%20unmissable%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flyrid-meteor-shower-will-reach-its-peak-heres-how-to-watch-2023-4%5C%22%3Emeteor%3C%2Fa%3E%20enthusiasts.%20You%20can%20expect%20up%20to%20100%20meteors%20per%20hour%20that%20leave%20long%20blazing%20trails%20and%20create%20%26quot%3Bfireballs%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20bright%20explosions%20that%20last%20longer%20than%20those%20made%20by%20typical%20meteors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20the%20number%20one%20producer%20of%20fireballs%20among%20all%20meteor%20showers%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Cooke.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20conditions%20are%20due%20to%20be%20particularly%20good%20for%20viewing%20because%20the%20moon%20will%20be%20at%20the%20very%20end%20of%20its%20crescent%20phase.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCompared%20to%20last%20year%20when%20the%20moon%20was%20full%2C%20this%20year%20is%20going%20to%20be%20great%2C%26quot%3B%20Cooke%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Perseids%20happen%20when%20Earth's%20orbit%20moves%20through%20space%20debris%20left%20behind%20by%20the%20comet%20Swift-Tuttle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERocky%20debris%20slams%20into%20our%20atmosphere%20at%2037%20miles%20per%20second%2C%20or%20about%20133%2C000%20mph%2C%20creating%20fiery%20streaks%20across%20the%20night%20sky.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20Perseids%20can%20be%20seen%20from%20anywhere%20Northern%20Hemisphere%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221885%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20big%20fireball%20is%20seen%20streaking%20over%20a%20lake%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20the%20day.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c8f253048ff200190ebaf9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Perseid%20m