is%20also%20one%20of%20India's%20foremost%20LGBT%20activists%2C%20described%20his%20own%20parents'%20attempt%20to%20%26quot%3Bconvert%26quot%3B%20him.%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20an%20absolute%20case%20of%20discrimination%20and%20violation%20of%20human%20rights.%20Whether%20I'm%20a%20prince%20or%20not%20a%20prince%2C%20parents%20have%20no%20right%20to%20put%20their%20children%20through%20%5Bthis%5D%20kind%20of%20torture%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gohil%20claimed%20that%20his%20parents%20visited%20doctors%20in%20the%20hope%20they%20could%20%26quot%3Bperform%20a%20surgery%20on%20my%20brain%2C%20and%20even%20make%20me%20undergo%20electroshock%20therapy%26quot%3B.%20However%2C%20as%20his%20parents%20planned%20for%20him%20to%20receive%20the%20treatments%20in%20the%20United%20States%20-%20where%20conversion%20therapy%20has%20been%20widely%20discredited%20-%20he%20was%20ultimately%20able%20to%20avoid%20being%20subjected%20to%20such%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFortunately%20for%20me%20and%20fortunately%20for%20them%20the%20American%20Psychiatric%20Association%20had%20said%20that%20homosexuality%20is%20not%20a%20mental%20disorder%2C%20so%20they%20were%20not%20successful%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Gohil%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fjose-paulino-gomes-from-brazil-believed-to-be-worlds-oldest-man-dies-at-127-4258287%5C%22%3EJose%20Paulino%20Gomes%20From%20Brazil%2C%20Believed%20To%20Be%20'World's%20Oldest%20Man'%2C%20Dies%20At%20127%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENevertheless%2C%20the%20Prince%20said%20that%20he%20suffered%20severe%20%26quot%3Bembarrassment%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bhumiliation%26quot%3B%20while%20enduring%20the%20%26quot%3Bpain%20and%20suffering%26quot%3B%20of%20his%20parents'%20futile%20attempts%20to%20change%20his%20sexual%20orientation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20didn't%20happen%20but%20imagine%20how%20