tnesses%20said%20a%20mob%20of%20around%20200%20had%20entered%20the%20area%20around%204%20pm%2C%20armed%20with%20sticks%20and%20stones.%20They%20vandalized%20several%20shops%2C%20including%20several%20meat%20shops%2C%20and%20set%20fire%20to%20a%20restaurant.%20No%20one%20was%20injured.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EViolence%20broke%20out%20during%20a%20religious%20procession%20yesterday%20in%20Nuh%20--%20just%2050%20km%20from%20Delhi%20--%20following%20what%20many%20say%20is%20an%20objectionable%20video%20that%20went%20viral.%20As%20a%20mob%20attacked%20the%20procession%20with%20stones%2C%20the%202%2C500-plus%20participants%20rushed%20into%20a%20temple%20to%20take%20shelter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20violence%20escalated%20as%20the%20evening%20progressed%20--%20a%20mosque%20was%20torched%20post-midnight%2C%20more%20than%20a%20hundred%20vehicles%20were%20torched%20and%20vandalised%20as%20mobs%20went%20on%20rampage%20in%20Nuh%20and%20neighbouring%20Gurugram.%20The%20dead%20include%20two%20security%20personnel%20and%20two%20civilians%2C%20one%20of%20them%20a%20cleric%20of%20the%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20people%20who%20had%20taken%20shelter%20in%20the%20temple%20were%20rescued%20close%20to%20midnight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20administration%2C%2044%20FIRs%20have%20been%20registered%20so%20far%20in%20which%20more%20than%2070%20people%20have%20been%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20violence%20started%20after%20rumours%20that%20Monu%20Manesar%2C%20a%20Bajrang%20Dal%20activist%20wanted%20over%20the%20murder%20of%20two%20men%20from%20Bharatpur%2C%20was%20attending%20the%20rally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMonu%20Manesar%20--%20on%20the%20run%20since%20Junaid%20and%20Nasir%20were%20beaten%20and%20burnt%20alive%20in%20their%20car%20in%20February%20--%20had%20asked%20people%20in%20a%20video%20to%20join%20the%20religious%20procession%20and%20claimed%20that%20he%20would%20attend%20it%20also.%20Sources%20said%20his%20associates%20had%20also%20given%20provoca