nts'%20money%20on%20%26quot%3Bexorbitant%20luxury%20goods%26quot%3B%2C%20per%20the%20SEC.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%20has%20just%20charged%20a%20crypto%20entrepreneur%20with%20illegally%20raising%20over%20%241%20billion%20in%20unregistered%20token%20offerings%2C%20before%20splurging%20over%20%2412%20million%20of%20that%20on%20luxury%20goods%20for%20himself.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERichard%20Schueler%2C%20known%20online%20as%20Richard%20Heart%2C%20spent%20customer%20funds%20on%20luxuries%20such%20as%20a%20white%20Ferrari%20Roma%20and%20rare%20Rolexes%20including%20a%20%24550%2C000%20Daytona%20%26quot%3BEye%20of%20the%20Tiger%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20%24800%2C000%20GMT-Master%20II%2C%20according%20to%20the%20SEC%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20most%20unconventional%20of%20all%20Schueler's%20purchases%20may%20be%20a%20billion-year%20old%20black%20diamond%2C%20nicknamed%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Enigma%26quot%3B%2C%20that%20may%20have%20come%20from%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20it%20all%20came%20crashing%20down%20in%20March%2C%20Schueler%20ran%20three%20unregistered%20securities%3A%20Hex%2C%20PulseChain%2C%20and%20PulseX.%20Per%20the%20SEC's%20lawsuit%2C%20Heart%20continually%20touted%20his%20investments%20as%20a%20pathway%20to%20%26quot%3Bgrandiose%20wealth%26quot%3B%2C%20declaring%20that%20Hex%2C%20for%20example%2C%20%26quot%3Bwas%20built%20to%20be%20the%20highest%20appreciating%20asset%20that%20has%20ever%20existed%20in%20the%20history%20of%20man.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHeart%20spent%20nearly%20%247.2%20million%20of%20PulseChain%20investor%20assets%20on%20luxury%20watches%20and%20high-end%20automobiles%20that%20he%20purchased%20in%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Finland%2C%20and%20Estonia%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20regulator%20said%20in%20the%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20%26quot%3BHeart%20misappropriated%20approximately%20%245%20million%20of%20PulseChain%20investor%20assets%2C%20sending%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20assets%20to%20Sotheby's%20in%20February%202022%20to%20purchase%20a%20555-carat%20black%20diamond%20called%20%26quot%3BThe%20Enigma%2C%26quot%3B%20purportedly%20the%20largest%20black%20diamond%20in%20the%20world.%20Heart%20purchased%20the%20diamond%20for%20%C2%A33%2C161%2C000%20(%244.28%20million%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20transaction)%2C%20funding%20the%20purchase%20by%20transferring%20both%20ETH%20and%20fiat%20currency%20to%20Sotheby's%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20SEC%20is%20on%20the%20warpath%20against%20the%20crypto%20sector%20this%20year.%20In%20the%20first%20half%20of%202023%20alone%2C%20it%20sued%20Binance%20for%20running%20an%20illegal%20exchange%2C%20accused%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried%20and%20his%20executives%20of%20paying%20themselves%20multi-million%20dollar%20bonuses%2C%20and%20engaged%20in%20a%20lengthy%20suit%20to%20determine%20whether%20XRP%20tokens%20could%20be%20deemed%20proper%20securities%20(they%20weren't%2C%20the%20court%20ruled).%20It%20also%20charged%20Gemini%2C%20Genesis%2C%20Tron%2C%20Bittrex%2C%20and%20the%20company%20behind%20TerraUSD.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHeart%2C%20Hex%2C%20PulseChain%2C%20and%20PulseX%20violated%20the%20federal%20securities%20laws%20through%20the%20unregistered%20offer%20and%20sale%20of%20securities.%20Additionally%2C%20through%20the%20misappropriation%20of%20investor%20assets%2C%20Heart%20and%20PulseChain%20defrauded%20their%20investors%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20regulator%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESEC%20chair%20Gary%20Gensler%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fcryptocurrency-rife-with-fraud-hucksters-warns-gary-gensler-sec-2023-7%5C%22%3Elast%20week%20called%20the%20cryptocurrency%20world%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3Brife%20with%20fraud%2C%20rife%20with%20hucksters%26quot%3B%2C%20as%20he%20roots%20out%20some%20of%20the%20worst%20crimes%20in%20the%20embattled%20sector.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20%26quot%3BEnigma%26quot%3B%20diamond%20is%