5-28%20and%2044%3A%20The%20Imperative%20for%20a%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F01170315%2FSeesaw-but-in-a-void.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20piece%20was%20originally%20published%20in%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3EIndia%20Cable%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20by%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3EThe%20Wire%C2%A0%3Cem%3Eand%20Galileo%20Ideas%3C%2Fem%3E.%C2%A0%3Cem%3ETo%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclick%20here%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EProponents%20of%20a%20uniform%20civil%20code%20(UCC)%20argue%20that%20it%20will%20promote%20equality%20and%20justice%2C%20while%20its%20opponents%20fear%20that%20it%20may%20lead%20to%20the%20erosion%20of%20minority%20rights%20and%20cultural%20diversity.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStriking%20an%20equilibrium%20between%20Articles%2025-28%20and%20Article%2044%20of%20the%20constitution%20while%20implementing%20the%20UCC%20is%20of%20utmost%20importance%20to%20ensure%20that%20this%20process%20is%20not%20just%20a%20political%20ploy%2C%20but%20the%20intellectually%20deliberated%20pursuit%20of%20harmonious%20governance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20need%20for%20a%20UCC%20must%20not%20be%20driven%20by%20emotional%20arguments%20of%20either%20the%20majority%20or%20minority%20communities%2C%20nor%20should%20it%20be%20a%20political%20charade.%20Instead%2C%20it%20must%20be%20approached%20with%20intellectual%20labour%20and%20rigorous%20deliberations%2C%20considering%20its%20implications%20on%20the%20diverse%20fabric%20of%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EArticle%2044%20of%20the%20constitution%2C%20which%20promotes%20the%20UCC%2C%20is%20a%20Directive%20Principle%20of%20State%20Policy%20(DPSP).%20These%20principles%20are%20guidelines%20for%20the%20government%20to%20achieve%20social%20and%20economic%20democracy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20UCC%2C%20as%20a%20DPSP%2C%20calls%20for%20taking%20into%20account%20the%20evolving%20nature%20of%20the%20country%20and%20its%20society.%20Any%20effort%20to%20implement%20the%20UCC%20should%20seek%20to%20preserve%20and%20respect%20the%20unique%20cultural%20identities%20of%20various%20communities.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20current%20political%20move%20found%20support%20in%20the%20judgement%20by%20Justices%20Kuldip%20Singh%20and%20R.M.%20Sahai%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F733037%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESarla%20Mudgal%20vs%20Union%20of%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(1995).%20In%20this%20landmark%20case%2C%20the%20judgement%C2%A0raised%20the%20question%20of%20a%20common%20civil%20code%20and%20its%20potential%20implications%20for%20the%20freedom%20of%20religion%20guaranteed%20by%20the%20constitution.%20The%20case%20remains%20a%20pivotal%20reference%20in%20the%20ongoing%20discourse%20about%20a%20UCC.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-knows-an-actual-ucc-will-be-an-electoral-disaster-for-him%5C%22%3ENarendra%20Modi%20Knows%20an%20Actual%20UCC%20Will%20Be%20an%20Electoral%20Disaster%20for%20Him%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESarla%20Mudgal%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20emphasises%20the%20need%20for%20a%20UCC%20as%20a%20solution%20to%20the%20issue%20raised%20in%20the%20case%2C%20holding%20that%20the%20second%20marriage%20of%20a%20Hindu%20husband%20after%20conversion%20to%20Islam%2C%20without%20dissolving%20his%20first%20marriage%20under%20law%2C%20to%20be%20invalid.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20court%2C%20emphasising%20on%20misuse%20of%20personal%20laws%2C%20reiterates%20that%20Article%2044%20of%20the%20Indian%20constitution%20mandates%20the%20state%20to%20secure%20a%20UCC%20for%20all%20its%20citizens.%20A%20well-implemented%20UCC%20can%20rectify%20such%20discrepancies%20and%20ensure%20gender%20justice%20and%20equal%20rights.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJustice%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20observation%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESarla%20Mudgal%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20highlights%20that%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20UCC%2C%20individuals%20might%20attempt%20to%20misuse%20religious%20freedoms%20to%20evade%20legal%20restrictions.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Sahai%20also%20opined%20that%20practices%20associated%20with%20different%20religions%20may%20appear%20excessive%20or%20conflicting%20to%20others%2C%20but%20they%20are%20matters%20of%20conscience%20and%20should%20be%20approached%20with%20respect.%20Reason%20and%20logic%20may%20not%20play%20a%20significant%20role%20in%20such%20matters%3B%20instead%2C%20emotions%20need%20to%20be%20tempered%20with%20sincere%20effort.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20need%20for%20a%20UCC%20is%20acknowledged%2C%20but%20its%20successful%20implementation%20requires%20the%20cooperation%20of%20enlightened%20individuals%2C%20statesmen%20and%20leaders%20who%20can%20create%20a%20conducive%20social%20climate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETheir%20stance%2C%20however%2C%20was%20strongly%20criticised%20by%20the%20distinguished%20constitutional%20lawyer%20H.M.%20Seervai%2C%20in%20an%20article%20titled%20%E2%80%98Uniform%20Civil%20Code%3A%20Judiciary%20Oversteps%20its%20Brief%E2%80%99%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%3B%20July%205%2C%201995).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20article%20highlighted%20that%20the%20judges%20had%20ventured%20beyond%20the%20scope%20of%20the%20case%20and%20addressed%20the%20idea%20of%20a%20common%20civil%20code.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EJustice%20Kuldip%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20argument%2C%20linking%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20UCC%20to%20Hindu%20men%20converting%20to%20Islam%20to%20marry%20multiple%20wives%2C%20was%20deemed%20specious.%20Justice%20Sahai%20dissented%20and%20emphasised%20that%20religion%20encompasses%20more%20than%20just%20faith%20and%20belief.%20The%20judges%20overlooked%20Article%20145(5)%2C%20requiring%20majority%20concurrence%2C%20rendering%20their%20opinion%20on%20the%20compatibility%20of%20a%20UCC%20with%20freedom%20of%20religion%20inconclusive.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESeervai%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20judiciary%20cannot%20enforce%20Article%2044%2C%20which%20calls%20for%20a%20UCC%2C%20as%20it%20falls%20under%20the%20purview%20of%20the%20executive%20and%20parliament.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20core%20principles%20behind%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20UCC%20is%20to%20ensure%20gender%20justice%20and%20equal%20rights.%20A%20well-crafted%20code%20should%20address%20discriminatory%20practices%20in%20personal%20laws%20and%20promote%20a%20more%20equitable%20society.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20the%20UCC%20must%20not%20be%20used%20as%20a%20tool%20to%20impose%20majority%20beliefs%20on%20minority%20communities%2C%20or%20to%20attack%20their%20cultural%20practices.%20A%20balanced%20approach%20that%20respects%20diversity%20and%20protects%20minority%20rights%20is%20crucial.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUpon%20examining%20the%20Constituent%20Assembly%20debates%2C%20it%20is%20evident%20that%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20believed%20in%20the%20significance%20of%20a%20UCC.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2FDr._Babasaheb_Ambedkar_chairman_of_the_Drafting_Committee_presenting_the_final_draft_of_the_Indian_Constitution_to_Dr._Rajendra_Prasad_on_25_November_1949.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22670%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-204340%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22526%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EDr%20B.R.%20Ambedkar%20(L)%20after%20presenting%20the%20constitution%20to%20the%20first%20president%20Dr%20Rajendra%20Prasad%20(R).%20Credit%3A%20Unknown%20author%2FWikimedia%20Commons.%20Public%20domain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20considering%20the%20Special%20Marriage%20Act%2C%20his%20stance%20on%20the%20importance%20of%20individual%20choice%20in%20matters%20of%20marriage%20aligns%20with%20the%20principles%20reflected%20in%20the%20Act.%20Ambedkar%20emphasised%20that%20a%20UCC%20should%20be%20implemented%20voluntarily%2C%20considering%20the%20sentiments%20and%20preferences%20of%20various%20religious%20communities%20in%20order%20to%20foster%20a%20harmonious%20evolution%20of%20a%20uniform%20civil%20law.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20inclusion%20of%20the%20UCC%20in%20the%20DPSP%20should%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20guiding%20principle%20for%20formulating%20laws%20and%20policies%2C%20rather%20than%20a%20strict%20mandate.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20current%20debates%20surrounding%20the%20UCC%20are%20often%20politically%20motivated.%20Instead%20of%20engaging%20in%20mere%20rhetoric%2C%20policymakers%20must%20focus%20on%20drafting%20a%20comprehensive%20law%20that%20considers%20the%20diverse%20religious%20freedoms%20and%20practices%20while%20ensuring%20constitutional%20objectives%20are%20met.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20quest%20for%20equilibrium%20between%20Articles%2025-28%20and%20Article%2044%20while%20implementing%20the%20uniform%20civil%20code%20is%20a%20multifaceted%20challenge.%20It%20requires%20intellectual%20rigour%2C%20unbiased%20deliberations%20and%20a%20deep%20understanding%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20diversity%20and%20cultural%20fabric.%20A%20well-crafted%20UCC%20can%20foster%20gender%20justice%2C%20equal%20rights%20and%20social%20harmony%2C%20without%20compromising%20the%20essence%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20unity%20in%20diversity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStriking%20this%20balance%20is%20essential%20for%20building%20a%20progressive%2C%20inclusive%20and%20just%20society%20for%20all%20citizens.%20Also%2C%20it%20is%20essential%20to%20recognise%20the%20significant%20value%20of%20Article%2025-28%20of%20the%20constitution%2C%20which%20enshrines%20the%20right%20to%20freedom%20of%20religion%20as%20a%20fundamental%20right.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20expectation%20from%20the%2022nd%20Law%20Commission%20is%20that%20it%20will%20adopt%20an%20impartial%2C%20consultative%20and%20attentive%20approach%20in%20understanding%20the%20complexities%20surrounding%20the%20uniform%20civil%20code%2C%20and%20consider%20the%20viewpoints%20of%20all%20relevant%20stakeholders%20before%20formulating%20any%20recommendations%20or%20proposals%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EAravindan%20Anandan%20is%20assistant%20professor%2C%20School%20of%20Legal%20Studies%20and%20Governance%2C%20Vidyashilp%20University%2C%20Bengaluru%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690891256000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F01170315%2FSeesaw-but-in-a-void.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fequilibrium-between-religious-freedom-and-ucc-dpsp%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Striking%20a%20balance%20between%20equality%20and%20religious%20freedom%20requires%20unbiased%20deliberation%20and%20intellectual%20rigour%2C%20but%20the%20current%20debates%20surrounding%20the%20UCC%20are%20often%20politically%20motivated.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fequilibrium-between-religious-freedom-and-ucc-dpsp%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Lazy%20girl%20jobs'%20put%20workers%20at%20risk%20of%20layoffs%20and%20sacrifice%20long-term%20job%20progression%2C%20career%20expert%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lazy%20girl%20jobs%20Gabrielle%20Judge%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6489ad1f01faff0019135cb9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20new%20%26quot%3Blazy%20girl%20job%26quot%3B%20trend%20has%20been%20widely%20shared%20on%20TikTok.%3Cp%3EGabrielle%20Judge%2FTikTok%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHaving%20a%20%26quot%3Blazy%20girl%20job%26quot%3B%20may%20put%20employees'%20longtime%20career%20progression%20at%20risk%2C%20an%20expert%20says.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMarc%20Cenedella%2C%20a%20careers%20expert%2C%20told%20Insider%20that%20companies%20are%20on%20the%20lookout%20for%20the%20trend.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BThe%20problem%20with%20having%20the%20lazy%20girl%20job%20is%20that%20they're%20the%20first%20ones%20to%20get%20laid%20off%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20a%20%26quot%3Blazy%20girl%20job%26quot%3B%20may%20put%20employees'%20longtime%20career%20progression%20at%20risk%2C%20a%20careers%20expert%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20%26quot%3Blazy%20girl%20job%26quot%3B%20trend%2C%20which%20has%20been%20widely%20shared%20on%20TikTok%2C%20is%20workers'%20latest%20revolt%20against%20corporate%20America.%20The%20term%20generally%20refers%20to%20a%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flazy-girl-job-trend-tiktok-explained-defending-low-stress-work-2023-7%23%3A~%3Atext%3DWomen%2520on%2520TikTok%2520are%2520saying%2Cin%2520a%2520May%252022nd%2520video.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elow-stress%20job%20that%20still%20pays%20well%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20was%20popularized%20by%20TikToker%20Gabrielle%20Judge%20back%20in%20May.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20as%20more%20workers%20took%20to%20the%20platform%20to%20brag%20about%20their%20low-key%20jobs%2C%20some%20started%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Ftiktok-lazy-girl-job-trend-corporate-snitching-backlash-fired-2023-7%3Finline-endstory-related-recommendations%3D%26_gl%3D1*677ve7*_ga*Nzg4MjgyNjAxLjE2NzM2MTAyNDA.*_ga_E21CV80ZCZ*MTY5MDg4NjEwMy41OTIuMS4xNjkwODg2Nzc1LjUyLjAuMA..%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworry%20about%20backlash%20from%20employers.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Marc%20Cenedella%2C%20a%20careers%20expert%20and%20founder%20of%20the%20job%20search%20site%20Ladders%2C%20companies%20are%20already%20wising%20up%20to%20the%20trend%20and%20on%20the%20lookout%20for%20workers%20in%20roles%20that%20are%20too%20lightweight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20on%20the%20front%20page%20of%20the%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BSo%20emails%20and%20memos%20are%20going%20around%20corporate%20America%20right%20now%20saying%2C%20hey%2C%20let's%20make%20sure%20we%20don't%20have%20lazy%20girl%20jobs%20in%20our%20companies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20supervisors%20are%20noticing%20the%20trend%20and%20could%20be%20looking%20more%20closely%20at%20teams%3A%20%26quot%3BCompanies%20are%20getting%20smarter%20and%20they're%20measuring%20output%20and%20productivity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECenedella%20said%20the%20trend%20is%20likely%20a%20direct%20consequence%20of%20how%20employees%20have%20been%20treated%20over%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20idea%20of%20not%20having%20so%20much%20loyalty%20to%20your%20employer%20is%20the%20natural%20consequence%20of%20everything%20that%20American%20business%20has%20done%20the%20last%2050%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20just%20a%20tit%20for%20tat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20not%20just%20a%20company%20bottom%20line%20the%20TikTok%20life%20hack%20might%20be%20hurting%2C%20Cenedella%20said%20that%20workers%20could%20also%20be%20sacrificing%20their%20own%20futures.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20problem%20with%20having%20the%20lazy%20girl%20job%20is%20that%20they're%20the%20first%20ones%20to%20get%20laid%20off%20when%20tough%20times%20come%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20these%20workers%20are%20also%20only%20%26quot%3Bcheating%20themselves%26quot%3B%20because%20they're%20not%20developing%20skills%20at%20work%2C%20which%20then%20stunts%20career%20progression.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20Cenedella%20advises%20committing%20to%20your%20job%20somewhat%20superficially%20and%20not%20giving%20or%20expecting%20too%20much%20loyalty%20from%20your%20employer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20far%20better%20to%20say%20%E2%80%94%20I'm%20only%20going%20to%20give%20six%20hours%20a%20day%20to%20this%20company.%20And%20I'm%20going%20to%20be%20realistic%20about%20what%20that%20means%20for%20me%20in%20terms%20of%20how%20loyal%20they're%20going%20to%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20okay%20to%20be%20lazy%20in%20your%20heart%20and%20not%20make%20an%20emotional%20commitment%20to%20your%20employer%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BBut%20you%20shouldn't%20be%20lazy%20on%20yourself%2C%20you%20should%20always%20be%20trying%20to%20make%20yourself%20better.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flazy-girl-jobs-tiktok-layoffs-risk-career-progression-getting-fired-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690891222000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c8e6d5048ff200190eb340%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flazy-girl-jobs-tiktok-layoffs-risk-career-progression-getting-fired-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Marc%20Cenedella%2C%20a%20careers%20expert%20and%20author%2C%20said%20companies%20are%20already%20wising%20up%20to%20the%20trend%20