ds%2F2023%2F07%2F25222448%2FSupreme-Court-1.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20taken%20a%20dim%20view%20of%20law%20enforcement%20and%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20handling%20of%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20Manipur%2C%20calling%20police%20investigation%20%E2%80%9Ctardy%E2%80%9D%20and%20asking%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20to%20be%20present%20in%20court%20on%20August%204%20to%20be%20able%20to%20answer%20judges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-manipur-violence-absolute-breakdown-of-machinery-of-state-in-manipur-no-law-order-summons-dgp-234099%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20bench%20of%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%2C%20Justice%20JB%20Pardiwala%20and%20Justice%20Manoj%20Misra%2C%20who%20are%20hearing%20a%20bunch%20of%20petitions%20on%20the%20Manipur%20violence%2C%20including%20those%20by%20victims%20of%20sexual%20violence%2C%20was%20%E2%80%9Caghast%E2%80%9D%20to%20learn%20that%20FIRs%20have%20not%20been%20registered%20for%20nearly%20three%20months%20after%20some%20occurrences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20learned%20that%20only%20a%20few%20arrests%20had%20been%20made%20in%20the%206%2C000%20FIRs%20that%20have%20been%20registered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBased%20on%20the%20preliminary%20data%2C%20it%20does%20prima%20facie%20appear%20that%20the%20investigation%20has%20been%20tardy.%20There%20has%20been%20a%20considerable%20lapse%20between%20the%20occurrence%20and%20the%20registration%20of%20FIRs%2C%20recording%20of%20witness%20statements%20and%20even%20the%20arrests%20are%20few%20and%20far%20between.%20In%20order%20to%20enable%20the%20court%20to%20appreciate%20the%20entire%20dimensions%20of%20the%20nature%20of%20investigation%20that%20is%20required%2C%20we%20direct%20the%20DGP%20of%20Manipur%20to%20be%20personally%20present%20in%20the%20Court%20at%20Friday%202%20PM%20and%20be%20in%20a%20position%20of%20answer%20the%20queries%20of%20the%20Court%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20apex%20court%20observed%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESolicitor%20General%20of%20India%20Tushar%20Mehta%2C%20appearing%20for%20Manipur%2C%20said%20he%20was%20not%20in%20a%20position%20to%20give%20details%20on%20how%20many%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9C6%2C532%20FIRs%E2%80%9D%20filed%20were%20%E2%80%9Czero%20FIRs%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESG%20Mehta%20also%20could%20not%20answer%20when%20the%20arrests%20in%20the%20case%20relating%20to%20the%20sexual%20violence%20video%20took%20place.%20As%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-video-arrest-biren-singh-supreme-court%5C%22%3Efirst%20arrest%20was%20announced%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20July%2020%2C%20after%20the%20video%20went%20viral%20and%20sparked%20nationwide%20outrage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20appears%20to%20be%2C%20subject%20to%20correction%2C%20after%20the%20video%20surfaced%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20SG%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CJI%20said%20that%20one%20thing%20was%20very%20clear%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20is%20such%20a%20long%20delay%20in%20filing%20FIRs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CJI%20also%20observed%20that%20few%20arrests%20have%20taken%20place%20with%20the%20exception%20of%20one%20of%20two%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInvestigation%20is%20so%20lethargic.%20FIRs%20registered%20after%20two%20months.%20Arrests%20not%20made.%20Statements%20recorded%20after%20a%20long%20lapse%20of%20time%E2%80%9D%2C%20CJI%20added%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CJI%20also%20said%20that%20this%20gives%20the%20judges%20the%20impression%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20was%20%5Bsuch%20an%5D%20absolute%20breakdown%20of%20machinery%20that%20you%20could%20not%20even