%20DGP%20doing%3F'%20is%20asked.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A40%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-manipur-violence-police%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Absolute%20Breakdown%20Of%20Constitutional%20Machinery%20In%20Manipur%3A%20Supreme%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20scathing%20remarks%20against%20the%20government%20over%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20in%20Manipur%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20today%20that%20there%20has%20been%20an%20absolute%20breakdown%20of%20constitutional%20machinery%20in%20the%20state%20for%20the%20past%20two%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETerming%20the%20investigation%20%26quot%3Btardy%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Blethargic%26quot%3B%2C%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%2C%20who%20is%20heading%20the%20bench%2C%20said%20there%20has%20been%20a%20delay%20in%20FIRs%20being%20registered%20and%20statements%20being%20recorded.%20The%20court%20has%20also%20demanded%20the%20personal%20presence%20of%20the%20Manipur%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20during%20the%20next%20hearing%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court's%20comments%20are%20likely%20to%20give%20further%20ammunition%20to%20the%20Opposition%2C%20which%20has%20been%20demanding%20the%20removal%20of%20Manipur%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Biren%20Singh%20and%20the%20imposition%20of%20President's%20Rule%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20hearing%20began%20this%20afternoon%2C%20Solicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%20informed%20the%20court%20that%206%2C523%20FIRs%20related%20to%20the%20violence%20have%20been%20registered%2C%20and%2011%20of%20these%20pertain%20to%20crimes%20against%20women%20and%20children.%20He%20said%20the%20data%20was%20part%20of%20a%20status%20report%20that%20he%20is%20submitting%20to%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mehta%20told%20the%20bench%20that%20seven%20people%2C%20including%20a%20juvenile%2C%20have%20been%20arrested%20in%20the%20case%20related%20to%20the%20horrific%20video%20of%20the%20women%20who%20were%20paraded%20naked%20and%20allegedly%20gang-raped.%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20asked%20whether%20the%20policemen%20accused%20of%20handing%20over%20the%20women%20to%20the%20mob%20have%20been%20interrogated%2C%20to%20which%20Mr%20Mehta%20said%20it%20may%20not%20be%20possible%20to%20get%20the%20information%20overnight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CJI%20then%20sought%20details%20of%20another%20incident%20in%20which%20two%20women%20were%20gang-raped%20and%20murdered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrefacing%20his%20answer%20with%20a%20disclaimer%20that%20they%20had%20gone%20through%20over%206%2C000%20FIRs%20in%20one%20night%20and%20there%20may%20be%20some%20errors%20in%20the%20data%2C%20Mr%20Mehta%20told%20the%20bench%20that%20a%20Zero%20FIR%20was%20registered%20on%20May%2015%20and%20it%20was%20converted%20into%20a%20regular%20FIR%20on%20June%2016.%20When%20the%20CJI%20asked%20whether%20any%20arrests%20had%20been%20made%2C%20the%20Solicitor%20General%20said%20he%20did%20not%20have%20information%20on%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20going%20through%20the%20report%20submitted%20by%20Mr%20Mehta%2C%20the%20CJI%20pointed%20out%20that%20an%20FIR%20was%20dated%20July%2026%20for%20an%20incident%20that%20happened%20on%20May%204.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BExcept%20for%20one%20or%20two%20cases%2C%20there%20are%20no%20arrests%20in%20other%20cases%3F%20The%20investigation%20is%20so%20lethargic.%20There%20has%20been%20a%20delay%20in%20filing%20FIRs%2C%20no%20arrests.%20For%20the%20past%20two%20months%2C%20has%20the%20situation%20not%20been%20conducive%20for%20even%20recording%20the%20statements%20of%20the%20victims%2C%26quot%3B%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20state%20police%20is%20incapable%20of%20investigation.%20They%20have%20lost%20control.%20There%20is%20absolutely%20no%20law%20and%20order...%20There%20has%20been%20an%20absolute%20breakdown%20of%20constitutional%20machinery%20in%20Manipur%20for%20the%20past%20two%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20an%20angry%20Chief%20Justice%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Solicitor%20General%20informed%20the%20court%20that%20252%20people%20had%20been%20arrested%20so%20far%20in%20connection%20with%20the%206%2C523%20FIRs.%20He%20assured%20the%20CJI%20that%20there%20won't%20be%20any%20lethargy%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20government%20and%20said%20that%20the%20centre%20was%20open%20to%20transferring%20all%2011%20FIRs%20to%20the%20CBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20about%206%2C500%20cases.%20We%20want%20to%20see%20the%20serious%20cases.%20You%20can't%20transfer%20everything%20to%20the%20CBI.%20We%20have%20to%20put%20a%20mechanism%20in%20place%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CJI%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoting%20that%20there%20have%20been%20150%20deaths%20in%20Manipur%20since%20the%20violence%20broke%20out%20on%20May%203%2C%20%C2%A0Justice%20Chandrachud%20said%20that%20the%20material%20provided%20to%20the%20court%20was%20inadequate.%20%26quot%3BState%20must%20carry%20out%20the%20exercise%20of%20break%20up%20of%20FIRs%2C%20how%20many%20FIRs%20concern%20murder%2C%20rape%2C%20arson%2C%20looting%2C%20outraging%20modesty%2C%20destruction%20of%20places%20of%20religious%20worship%20and%20grievous%20hurt%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20then%20ordered%20the%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20to%20be%20present%20during%20the%20next%20hearing%20on%20Monday%20and%20asked%20him%20to%20have%20the%20following%20information%20ready%20on%20each%20of%20the%20FIRs%3A%20date%20of%20occurrence%20of%20incident%3B%20date%20of%20registration%20of%20Zero%20FIR%3B%20date%20of%20registration%20of%20regular%20FIR%3B%20date%20on%20which%20witness%20statements%20were%20recorded%3B%20date%20on%20which%20statements%20under%20Section%20164%20of%20the%20Criminal%20Procedure%20Code%20(CrPC)%20were%20recorded%3B%20and%20date%20on%20which%20arrests%20were%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Chandrachud%20said%20the%20court%20may%20think%20of%20constituting%20a%20committee%20of%20former%20high%20court%20judges.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20just%20thinking%20out%20loud%20so%20there%20are%20no%20surprises%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20had%20also%20posed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsupreme-court-on-manipur-viral-video-manipur-women-paraded-naked-manipur-viral-video-incident-not-isolated-chief-justice-asks-how-many-firs-registered-4254901%5C%22%3Etough%20questions%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20the%20government%20during%20the%20hearing%20yesterday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20gainsaying%20the%20fact%20that%20crimes%20against%20women%20are%20taking%20place%20in%20all%20parts.%20You%20cannot%20excuse%20what%20is%20taking%20place%20in%20one%20part%20of%20the%20country%2C%20like%20Manipur%2C%20on%20the%20ground%20that%20similar%20crimes%20are%20happening%20in%20other%20parts%20too...%20Are%20you%20saying%20protect%20all%20daughters%20of%20India%20or%20don't%20protect%20anyone%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20CJI%20had%20asked%20when%20a%20lawyer%20had%20brought%20up%20crimes%20against%20women%20in%20Bengal%2C%20Rajasthan%20and%20Chhattisgarh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20has%20led%20to%20a%20logjam%20in%20Parliament%2C%20with%20both%20Houses%20being%20repeatedly%20adjourned%20since%20the%20monsoon%20session%20began%20on%20July%2020.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690890420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fvp0omcpg_supreme-court-manipur-crime-split-650_650x400_20_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fabsolute-breakdown-of-constitution-machinery-in-manipur-supreme-court-4258590%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20scathing%20remarks%20against%20the%20Manipur%20government%20over%20the%20violence%20in%20the%20state%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20today%20that%20there%20has%20been%20an%20absolute%20breakdown%20