-projects-in-pune%2Farticleshow%2F102314684.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20on%20Tuesday%20said%20it%20was%20a%20memorable%20moment%20for%20him%20to%20be%20conferred%20with%20Lokmanya%20Tilak%20National%20Award.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A38%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fpune%2Fpm-narendra-modi-flags-off-metro-trains-inaugurates-various-projects-in-pune%2Farticleshow%2F102314684.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20Justice%20Rohini%20Panel%20Submits%20Report%2C%20Will%20the%20Modi%20Govt%20Move%20Ahead%20with%20Sub-Quotas%20for%20OBCs%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2F22141813%2Fnalsar-final.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3ESix%20years%20after%20it%20was%20constituted%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpanel-for-obc-sub-categorisation-gets-its-14th-extension%5C%22%3Efollowing%2014%20extensions%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Rohini%20Commission%2C%20tasked%20with%20the%20sub-categorisation%20of%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%2C%20submitted%20its%20report%20to%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20on%20Monday%2C%20July%2031.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20commission%20report%20submitted%2C%20the%20ball%20is%20now%20in%20the%20court%20of%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20on%20whether%20or%20not%20it%20would%20want%20to%20apportion%20the%20existing%2027%25%20reservation%20among%20various%20groups%20which%20are%20part%20of%20the%20OBCs.%20The%20Commission%20was%20constituted%20in%20October%202017%20by%20the%20Modi%20government%20amid%20expectations%20that%20it%20would%20lead%20to%20the%20sub-division%20of%20the%20reservation%20pool%20among%20OBC%20communities%20depending%20upon%20the%20population%20and%20deprivation%20of%20particular%20communities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20has%20been%20a%20complaint%20among%20relatively%20backward%20communities%20among%20OBCs%20that%20those%20OBC%20groups%20with%20relatively%20good%20economic%20standing%20and%20educational%20standards%20have%20been%20grabbing%20the%20benefits%20of%20reservations%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20most%20deprived%20communities.%20The%20sub-grouping%2C%20many%20believe%2C%20would%20lead%20to%20equitable%20distribution%20of%20reservation%20benefits%20among%20the%20constituent%20groups.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20Commission%20was%20to%20submit%20its%20report%20in%2012%20weeks%2C%20following%20its%20constitution%20in%20October%202017%2C%20it%20has%20been%20given%2014%20extensions%20and%20its%20tenure%20finally%20ended%20on%20Monday%2C%20July%2031.%20It%20is%20widely%20believed%20that%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%2C%20following%20the%20constitution%20of%20the%20commission%2C%20had%20a%20rethink%20on%20the%20issue%2C%20for%20such%20a%20move%20to%20divide%20the%20reservation%20pool%20among%20OBCs%20could%20trigger%20controversy%20and%20affect%20its%20political%20fortunes.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20BJP%20government%20has%20dragged%20its%20feet%20on%20the%20issue%20for%20a%20long%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20Rohini%20Commission%20has%20submitted%20its%20report%20at%20a%20time%20when%20there%20is%20a%20growing%20clamour%20from%20the%20opposition%20parties%20to%20conduct%20a%20nationwide%20census%20assumes%20significance.%20The%20BJP%20has%20been%20opposed%20to%20the%20idea%20of%20caste%20census.%20In%20fact%2C%20Mandalite%20parties%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%2C%20have%20said%20if%20the%20government%20intends%20to%20go%20for%20division%20of%20the%20reservation%20pool%20among%20the%20OBCs%2C%20it%20should%20first%20carry%20out%20caste%20census%20to%20obtain%20information%20on%20the%20population%20share%20of%20constituent%20groups%20among%20the%20OBCs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20government%20notification%2C%20the%20commission%20headed%20by%20retired%20Justice%20G.%20Rohini%20of%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20was%20also%20tasked%20with%20recommending%20the%20correction%20of%20any%20repetitions%2C%20ambiguities%2C%20inconsistencies%2C%20and%20errors%20of%20spelling%20or%20transcription%2C%20examining%20the%20extent%20of%20inequitable%20distribution%20of%20benefits%20of%20reservation%20among%20the%20OBCs%2C%20and%20working%20out%20the%20mechanism%2C%20criteria%2C%20norms%20and%20parameters%20in%20a%20scientific%20approach%2C%20for%20sub-categorisation%20within%20such%20OBCs%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fdelhi%2Frohini-commission-examining-sub-categorisation-obc-report-president-8870799%2F%5C%22%3EPTI%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690889438000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2F22141813%2Fnalsar-final.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fas-justice-rohini-panel-submits-report-will-the-modi-govt-move-ahead-with-sub-quotas-for-obcs%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Commission%20formed%20in%20October%202017%20was%20tasked%20with%20examining%20the%20extent%20of%20inequitable%20distribution%20of%20benefits%20of%20reservation%20among%20the%20OBCs.%20It%20finally%20submitted%20its%20report%20on%20Monday%2C%20after%2014%20extensions.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fas-justice-rohini-panel-submits-report-will-the-modi-govt-move-ahead-with-sub-quotas-for-obcs%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Karthik%20Digs%20Up%20Stunning%20Ashes%20Stat%2C%20Earns%20'Honorary%20Englishman'%20Tag%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Day%204%20of%20the%20fifth%20Ashes%20Test%20between%20Australia%20and%20England%2C%20ended%20in%20the%20favour%20of%20the%20visitors%20as%20their%20score%20read%20at%20135%2F0%2