%20to%20The%20Washington%20Post.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20real-estate%20agent%20in%20Canada%20has%20been%20fined%2020%2C000%20Canadian%20dollars%2C%20the%20equivalent%20of%20%2415%2C087%2C%20after%20a%20home%20surveillance%20camera%20caught%20him%20drinking%20milk%20straight%20from%20a%20container%20at%20a%20seller's%20house%20and%20then%20putting%20it%20back%20in%20the%20fridge%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Fnation%2F2023%2F08%2F01%2Freal-estate-agent-drinking-milk%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20agent%2C%20Mike%20Rose%2C%20was%20waiting%20to%20show%20a%20house%20in%20Kamloops%2C%20British%20Columbia%2C%20to%20potential%20buyers%20in%20July%20last%20year%20when%20the%20homeowner%2C%20Lyska%20Fullerton%2C%20left%20the%20property%2C%20per%20The%20Post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%20in%20the%20day%2C%20Fullerton%20decided%20to%20check%20her%20Ring%20camera%2C%20expecting%20to%20see%20Rose%20giving%20a%20home%20tour%20to%20a%20group%20of%20prospective%20buyers%2C%20she%20told%20The%20Post.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20to%20her%20surprise%20she%20saw%20footage%20of%20Rose%20walking%20into%20the%20kitchen%2C%20taking%20a%20carton%20of%20milk%20out%20of%20her%20fridge%2C%20and%20drinking%20from%20it%2C%20before%20putting%20it%20back%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFullerton%20said%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Butterly%20speechless%2C%20in%20shock%2C%20and%20creeped%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20largely%20because%20the%20incident%20took%20place%20while%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20was%20still%20a%20major%20source%20of%20concern.%20The%20pandemic%20had%20killed%20both%20her%20parents%20and%20her%20parents-in-law%2C%20she%20said%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20homeowner%2C%20the%20surveillance%20footage%20also%20showed%20Rose%20lounging%20on%20her%20couch%20and%20accidentally%20breaking%20its%20arm%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20was%20unprofessional%20in%20so%20many%20ways%2C%26quot%3B%20Fullerton%20told%20The%20Post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20part%20of%20it%20was%20just%20such%20an%20invasion%20of%20privacy%20and%20such%20an%20invasion%20of%20our%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFullerton%20said%20she%20confronted%20Rose%20two%20days%20after%20the%20incident%20and%20asked%20him%20if%20he%20had%20anything%20he%20wanted%20to%20tell%20her%2C%20per%20The%20Post.%20The%20newspaper%20reported%20that%20Fullerton%20said%20Rose%20replied%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20milk%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%2C%20Fullerton%20reported%20the%20agent%2C%20explaining%20to%20The%20Post%20that%20it%20wasn't%20so%20much%20about%20the%20milk%2C%20but%20more%20that%20the%20agent%20had%20failed%20to%20disclose%20his%20actions%20to%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20didn't%20even%20leave%20a%20note%20or%20tell%20us%20this%20happened.%20I%20had%20to%20find%20out%20because%20of%20my%20camera%2C%20and%20that's%20just%20gross%20and%20plain%20wrong%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20makes%20you%20question%20your%20trust%20in%20people%20who%20visit%20your%20home.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2018%2C%20the%20British%20Columbia%20Financial%20Services%20Authority%20seemingly%20agreed%2C%20deeming%20Rose's%20actions%20%26quot%3Bunbecoming%26quot%3B%20behavior%20that%20undermined%20the%20reputation%20of%20the%20real%20estate%20industry%2C%20citing%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bclaws.gov.bc.ca%2Fcivix%2Fdocument%2Fid%2Fcomplete%2Fstatreg%2F04042_01%23part1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBritish%20Columbia%20Real%20Estate%20Services%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20per%20The%20Post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20fine%2C%20the%20agency%20ordered%20him%20to%20pay%202%2C500%20Canadian%20dollars%2C%20or%20%241%2C886%2C%20in%20enforcement%20expenses%2C%20records%20reviewed%20by%20The%20Post%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERose%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment%2C%20but%20in%20his%20defense%2C%20he%20told%20the%20government%20agency%20that%20he%20was%20unusually%20dehydrated%20at%20the%20time%20due%20to%20new%20medication%20and%20stress%2C%20according%20to%20The%20Post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20provided%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcfjctoday.com%2F2022%2F07%2F20%2Fkamloops-realtor-suspended-after-being-caught-on-camera-drinking-milk-from-clients-fridge%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0itHlyVZfQJ3UuVpyMNYgmJzDwUYDTK_yUaHzaoBH9eOl57x1WDgaDWkI%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECFJC%20Today%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20Rose%20apologized%20for%20his%20%26quot%3Bvery%20unfortunate%2C%20and%20very%20uncharacteristic%2C%20decision%20to%20drink%20milk%20from%20a%20container%20from%20the%20homeowners'%20fridge.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20never%20done%20this%20kind%20of%20thing%20before%2C%20nor%20will%20I%20ever%20behave%20in%20this%20way%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20acted%20in%20a%20way%20that%20is%20unbecoming%20of%20my%20brokerage%20firm%20and%20my%20fellow%20realtors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-agent-fined-15k-gulping-milk-homeowners-house-realtor-2023-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690888420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64c8d803cf07780019683714%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-agent-fined-15k-gulping-milk-homeowners-house-realtor-2023-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20homeowner%20captured%20a%20real-estate%20agent%20drinking%20milk%20out%20of%20a%20carton%20from%20her%20fridge.%20A%20government%20agency%20fined%20him%20for%20%26quot%3Bunbecoming%26quot%3B%20behavior.%22%2C%22au