A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20that%20would%20replace%20the%20Delhi%20Services%20Ordinance%20%E2%80%93%20giving%20the%20Centre%20control%20over%20the%20postings%20and%20transfers%20of%20Delhi%20bureaucrats%20--%20contains%20three%20key%20changes%2C%20one%20of%20which%20offers%20some%20respite%20to%20the%20Delhi%20assembly%20in%20terms%20of%20legislation.%20A%20portion%20that%20prevented%20the%20assembly%20from%20creating%20laws%20on%20%26quot%3BState%20Public%20Services%20and%20State%20Public%20Service%20Commission%26quot%3B%20has%20been%20removed.%20The%20power%20granted%20to%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20to%20appoint%20chiefs%20of%20all%20bodies%2C%20boards%20and%20corporations%20has%20also%20been%20curbed.%20He%20will%20now%20deal%20only%20with%20bodies%20set%20up%20through%20an%20act%20of%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%2C%20which%20had%20become%20a%20huge%20political%20flashpoint%20between%20the%20government%20and%20the%20opposition%2C%20has%20been%20tabled%20in%20parliament%20today.%20The%20debate%20on%20it%20is%20due%20tomorrow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opposition%20--%20unitedly%20opposing%20the%20bill%20through%20the%20efforts%20of%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%C2%A0%20--%20is%20fighting%20the%20bill%20tooth%20and%20nail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20government%2C%20which%20is%20already%20in%20a%20comfortable%20position%20in%20the%20upper%20house%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20can%20now%20count%20on%20the%20support%20of%20Odisha's%20ruling%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh's%20ruling%20YSR%20Congress.%20The%20BJD%2C%20which%20was%20expected%20to%20back%20the%20bill%2C%20formally%20announced%20its%20decision%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20bill%2C%20a%20copy%20of%20which%20is%20with%20NDTV%2C%20has%20significant%20omissions%20compared%20to%20the%20Ordinance%20brought%20in%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Section%203A%2C%20which%20was%20part%20of%20the%20Ordinance%2C%20has%20been%20removed%20completely.%20With%20this%20section%2C%20the%20Ordinance%20removed%20the%20Delhi%20Assembly's%20powers%20to%20make%20laws%20related%20to%20services%3Cbr%3E%5CnProvisions%20under%20another%20Section%20--%2045%20D%20of%20the%20Ordinance%20-%20has%20been%20diluted.%20This%20Section%20is%20related%20to%20the%20appointments%20made%20for%20Boards%2C%20Commissions%2C%20authorities%20and%20other%20statutory%20bodies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ordinance%20provided%20the%20LG%2FPresident%20with%20exclusive%20powers%20to%20make%20appointments%20to%20or%20nominate%20members%2F%20chairperson%20of%20all%20bodies%2C%20boards%2C%20corporations.%20The%20proposed%20bill%20provides%20this%20power%20to%20the%20LG%2FPresident%20only%20for%20bodies%2Fboards%2Fcommissions%20set%20up%20through%20an%20act%20of%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ordinance%20was%20brought%20in%20by%20the%20Central%20government%20on%20May%2019%2C%20days%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20declared%20that%20the%20elected%20government%20is%20the%20boss%20of%20Delhi%20and%20its%20powers%20will%20extend%20over%20everything%20except%20police%2C%20public%20order%20and%20land.%20It%20was%20a%20huge%20relief%20for%20the%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20government%2C%20which%20has%20been%20at%20loggerheads%20with%20the%20Centre%20--%20and%20its%20representative%2C%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20--%20over%20the%20control%20of%20the%20national%20capital%20ever%20since%20it%20came%20to%20power%20in%202015%20with%20a%20huge%20mandate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20declared%20that%20the%20Centre%20had%20%26quot%3Bdeceived%26quot%3B%20the%20people%20of%20Delhi%20with%20the%20introduction%20of%20the%20Ordinance.%20It%20also%20argued%20that%20if%20a%20precedent%20is%20set%20in%20Delhi%2C%20no%20elected%20government%20is%20safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20himself%2C%20along%20with%20party%20colleague%20and%20Punjab%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann%2C%20had%20visited%20most%20non-BJP%20ruled%20states%20and%20met%20opposition%20leaders%2C%20seeking%20their%20support%20to%20oppose%20the%20legislation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690888140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2Frth526i8_vk-saxena-kejriwal_625x300_20_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-to-make-all-rules-related-to-bureaucrats-says-delhi-services-bill-4258710%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20bill%20that%20would%20replace%20the%20Delhi%20Services%20ordinance%20giving%20the%20Centre%20control%20over%20the%20postings%20and%20transfers%20of%20Delhi%20bureaucrats%20--%20contains%20three%20key%20changes%20one%20of%20which%20offers%20some%20respite%20to%20the%20Delhi%20assembly%20in%20terms%20of%20legislation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-to-make-all-rules-related-to-bureaucrats-says-delhi-services-bill-4258710%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-to-make-all-rules-related-to-bureaucrats-says-delhi-services-bill-4258710%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-to-make-all-rules-related-to-bureaucrats-says-delhi-services-bill-4258710%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Xi%20Jinping%20Calls%20Project%20Through%20PoK%20%5C%22Testament%20Of%20Friendship%5C%22%20With%20Pak%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EChina%20will%20continue%20to%20work%20with%20its%20all-weather%20ally%20Pakistan%20to%20take%20their%20strategic%20ties%20to%20new%20heights%2C%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20has%20said%20as%20the%20two%20countries%20celebrated%20the%2010th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20launch%20of%20the%20ambitious%20so-called%20%26quot%3BCPEC%26quot%3B%20infrastructure%20projects%20in%20the%20South%20Asian%20country%20for%20regional%20connectivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20congratulatory%20message%20to%20the%20'Decade%20of%20China-Pakistan%20Economic%20Corridor'%20(CPEC)%20celebration%20event%20held%20in%20Islamabad%20on%20Monday%2C%20Xi%20said%20the%20USD%2060%20billion%20CPEC%20infrastructure%20programme%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Bimportant%20pioneering%20project%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative%20(BRI).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20so-called%20%26quot%3BCPEC%26quot%3B%2C%20which%20connects%20Gwadar%20Port%20in%20Pakistan's%20Balochistan%20with%20China's%20Xinjiang%20province%2C%20is%20opposed%20by%20India%20as%20it%20is%20being%20laid%20through%20Pakistan-occupied%20Kashmir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20was%20attended%20by%20Chinese%20Vice%20Premier%20He%20Lifeng%2C%20who%20is%20on%20a%20three-day%20visit%20to%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChina%20will%20work%20with%20Pakistan%20to%20aim%20for%20high-standard%2C%20sustainable%20and%20livelihood-enhancing%20outcomes%20and%20further%20build%20the%20CPEC%20into%20an%20exemplary%20project%20of%20high-quality%20Belt%20and%20Road%20cooperation%2C%26quot%3B%20Xi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSince%20its%20launch%20in%202013%2C%20China%20and%20Pakistan%20have%20been%20advancing%20CPEC%20under%20the%20principle%20of%20extensive%20consultation%2C%20joint%20contribution%20and%20shared%20benefits%2C%20and%20have%20achieved%20a%20number%20of%20early%20harvests%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20the%20state-run%20Xinhua%20news%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EXi%2C%20also%20the%20General%20Secretary%20of%20the%20ruling%20Communist%20Party%20of%20China%2C%20said%20the%20so-called%20%26quot%3BCPEC%26quot%3B%20has%20added%20new%20impetus%20to%20the%20economic%20and%20social%20development%20of%20Pakistan%20and%20laid%20a%20good%20foundation%20for%20regional%20connectivity%20and%20integration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20project%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bvivid%20testament%20to%20the%20all-weather%20friendship%20between%20China%20and%20Pakistan%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20provides%20an%20important%20underpinning%20for%20building%20an%20even%20closer%20China-Pakistan%20community%20with%20a%20shared%20future%20in%20the%20new%20era.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStressing%20that%20China%20and%20Pakistan%20will%20continue%20to%20improve%20overall%20planning%20and%20expand%20and%20deepen%20cooperation%2C%20Xi%20said%20no%20matter%20how%20the%20international%20landscape%20may%20change%2C%20China%20will%20always%20stand%20firmly%20with%20Pakistan%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChina%20and%20Pakistan%20will%20continue%20to%20work%20hand%20in%20hand%20and%20forge%20ahead%20in%20solidarity%20to%20carry%20forward%20the%20ironclad%20friendship%2C%20coordinate%20development%20and%20security%2C%26quot%3B%20Xi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20two%20countries%20will%20continue%20to%20%26quot%3Bpursue%20the%20cooperation%20of%20higher%20standards%2C%20broader%20scope%20and%20greater%20depth%2C%20and%20take%20the%20China-Pakistan%20all-weather%20strategic%20cooperative%20partnership%20to%20new%20heights%2C%20so%20as%20to%20make%20an%20even%20greater%20contribution%20to%20peace%20and%20prosperity%20in%20the%20two%20countries%20and%20the%20broader%20region%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20agreement%20for%20the%20so-called%20%26quot%3BCPEC%26quot%3B%20project%20was%20agreed%20in%202013%20but%20it%20was%20formally%20launched%20when%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20visited%20Pakistan%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BRI%20was%20launched%20by%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20in%202013.%20It%20aims%20to%20link%20Southeast%20Asia%2C%20Central%20Asia%2C%20the%20Gulf%20region%2C%20Africa%20and%20Europe%20with%20a%20network%20of%20land%20and%20sea%20routes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BRI%20is%20seen%20as%20an%20attempt%20by%20China%20to%20further%20its%20influence%20abroad%20with%20infrastructure%20projects%20funded%20by%20Chinese%20investments%20all%20over%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initiative%20also%20led%20to%20allegations%20of%20smaller%20countries%20reeling%