acter%20whose%20Janus-like%20nature%20is%20to%20look%20backwards%20even%20as%20he%20is%20compelled%20to%20walk%20forwards.%20This%20is%20the%20mild-mannered%20Alif%2C%20a%20history%20schoolteacher%20who%20subjects%20every%20free%20moment%20to%20a%20historical%20test%3A%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20now%20but%20how%20was%20it%20back%20then%3F%20Or%20that%20was%20then%20but%20how%20does%20it%20matter%20now%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETo%20his%20students%2C%20he%20tries%20to%20drive%20home%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20difference%20between%20history%20and%20story%E2%80%9D%20while%20being%20aware%20that%20%E2%80%9Cour%20stories%20are%20still%20swollen%20with%20the%20exaggerations%20that%20make%20some%20men%20impossibly%20broad-chested%20and%20lion-hearted%20and%20the%20rest%20just%20men%E2%80%9D.%20During%20a%20school%20trip%20to%20Humayun%E2%80%99s%20Tomb%2C%20one%20of%20his%20pupils%20addresses%20him%20with%20a%20religious%20slur%20and%2C%20instinctively%20and%20uncharacteristically%2C%20Alif%20responds%20by%20reaching%20out%20and%20twisting%20his%20ear.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20reverberations%20of%20this%20act%20are%20the%20framework%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20novel.%20However%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHistory%E2%80%99s%20Angel%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3Eis%20not%20simply%20a%20linear%20progression%20of%20events%3A%20it%20is%20an%20informed%20exploration%20of%20Alif%E2%80%99s%20milieu%2C%20with%20his%20family%20and%20friends%20providing%20the%20necessary%20shades%20and%20contrasts%20for%20a%20portrayal%20of%20a%20cross-section%20of%20Muslims%20in%20north%20India%20today.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOthers%20on%20this%20spectrum%20of%20faith%20and%20hope%20include%20Alif%E2%80%99s%20wife%20Tahira%2C%20a%20store%20manager%20at%20a%20Karol%20Bagh%20supermarket%20who%20is%20studying%20for%20an%20MBA%20and%20whose%20weekends%20are%20given%20over%20to%20%E2%80%9Cthat%20which%20makes%20the%20world%20go%20round%2C%20or%20so%20say%20Dale%20Carnegie%20and%20Steven%20Covey%E2%80%9D.%20Their%20teenage%20son%20often%20puzzles%20Alif%20by%20his%20fascination%20with%20technology%20and%20the%20digital%20world%2C%20as%20does%20the%20attitude%20of%20his%20practical%20cousin%2C%20owner%20of%20a%20shoe%20store%2C%20who%20dreams%20of%20moving%20to%20the%20Emirates%20and%20urges%20Alif%20to%20manage%20the%20shop%20in%20his%20place.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFurther%20ripples%20on%20the%20surface%20of%20Alif%E2%80%99s%20existence%20arrive%20in%20the%20form%20of%20ups%20and%20downs%20in%20the%20tempestuous%20life%20of%20his%20close%20friend%20Ganesh%2C%20who%20is%20a%20bit%20too%20fond%20of%20the%20bottle.%20Ganesh%20nurtures%20feelings%20for%20an%20old%20school%20crush%20and%2C%20to%20his%20surprise%2C%20Alif%20finds%20himself%20feeling%20the%20same%20way.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20ageing%20parents%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20do%20the%20best%20they%20can%20to%20survive%20in%20changing%20circumstances.%20Much%20of%20their%20time%20is%20spent%20in%20keeping%20tabs%20on%20relatives%2C%20friends%2C%20and%20their%20increasingly%20radicalised%20domestic%20help.%20The%20rest%20is%20spent%20in%20watching%20cooking%20shows%20and%20news%20on%20TV%2C%20with%20the%20latter%20inevitably%20posing%20the%20question%3A%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20does%20it%20mean%2C%20sir%2C%20to%20be%20a%20Muslim%20in%20contemporary%20India%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fislam-christianity-conversion-hindutva-violence%5C%22%3ENo%20Country%20for%20Religious%20Converts%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETheir%20lives%20are%20suffused%20by%20a%20feeling%20that%20Orhan%20Pamuk%20once%20described%20as%20%3Cem%3Eh%C3%BCz%C3%BCn%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20sense%20of%20melancholy.%20This%2C%20in%20his%20words%2C%20softens%20the%20view%20%E2%80%9Clike%20the%20condensation