20announced%20its%20support%20to%20the%20government%20on%20the%20critical%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20halfway%20mark%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20is%20120%2C%20if%20all%20238%20existing%20members%20vote%20that%20day.%20The%20full%20strength%20of%20the%20House%20is%20245%2C%20but%20there%20are%20seven%20vacancies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20and%20allies%20in%20the%20ruling%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance%20(NDA)%20have%20103%20members.%20The%20ruling%20party%20is%20also%20confident%20of%20the%20support%20of%20five%20nominated%20and%20one%20independent%20MPs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20support%20from%20BJD%20and%20YSRCP%2C%20the%20BJP-led%20government%20has%20127.%20Sources%20say%C2%A0N%20Chandrababu%20Naidu-led%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20and%20Mayawati's%20BSP%2C%20which%20have%20one%20MP%20each%20in%20the%20upper%20house%2C%20are%20also%20likely%20to%20support%20the%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20109%20MPs%20comprising%20those%20from%20the%2026-member%20opposition%20alliance%20INDIA%2C%20and%20some%20Independents%20such%20as%20Kapil%20Sibal%2C%20are%20expected%20to%20vote%20against%20the%20bill%2C%20which%20will%20replace%20the%20controversial%20Delhi%20services%20ordinance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20the%2026%20parties%20from%20the%20opposition%20grouping%2C%20at%20least%2018%20have%20a%20presence%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20and%20have%20101%20MPs%20collectively.%20Besides%20this%20bloc%2C%20the%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20(BRS)%20on%20Monday%20issued%20a%20whip%20to%20its%20seven%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MPs%20to%20be%20present%20in%20the%20House%20and%20vote%20against%20the%20bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Government%20of%20National%20Capital%20Territory%20of%20Delhi%20(Amendment)%20bill%20replaces%20an%20ordinance%20for%20the%20control%20of%20Delhi's%20bureaucrats%2C%20which%20was%20issued%20by%20the%20Centre%20to%20override%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20order%20that%20said%20the%20elected%20government%20in%20Delhi%2C%20not%20the%20Centre%2C%20has%20control%20over%20the%20transfer%20and%20appointments%20of%20bureaucrats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Central%20government%20will%20make%20all%20the%20rules%20related%20to%20bureaucrats%20in%20Delhi%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Delhi%20Services%20Bill%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-to-make-all-rules-related-to-bureaucrats-says-delhi-services-bill-4258710%5C%22%3Eaccessed%20exclusively%20by%20NDTV.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20says%20the%20Central%20government%20is%20empowered%20to%20make%20rules%20on%20matters%20related%20to%20the%20tenure%2C%20salaries%2C%20transfers%20or%20posting%20of%20officers%20in%20Delhi.%20The%20Centre%20will%20also%20have%20the%20power%20to%20decide%20on%20any%20action%20or%20probe%20against%20officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20amendment%20bill%20related%20to%20the%20services%20has%20some%20significant%20omissions%20compared%20to%20the%20ordinance%20brought%20in%20on%20May%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690884600000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2019-06%2Faja4t2t_narendra-modi-naveen-patnaik-pti_625x300_11_June_19.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-setback-for-aap-naveen-patnaiks-bjd-to-back-centre-on-delhi-services-bill-4258698%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi%20services%20Bill%3A%20The%20decision%20of%20Odisha's%20ruling%20party%2C%20which%20has%20nine%20MPs%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20will%20help%20the%20government%20touch%20the%20halfway%20mark%20in%20the%20upper%20house%2C%20where%20the%20BJP-led%20NDA%20does%20not%20have%20full%20majority%20on%20its%20own.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-setback-for-aap-naveen-patnaiks-bjd-to-back-centre-on-delhi-services-bill-4258698%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-setback-for-aap-naveen-patnaiks-bjd-to-back-centre-on-delhi-services