E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Chief%20Justice%20K.%C2%A0Vinod%20Chandran%20and%20Justice%20Partha%20Sarthy%20delivered%20its%20on%20five%20petitions%20challenging%20the%20survey.%20On%20July%207%2C%20the%20court%20had%20reserved%20its%20order%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Nitish%20Kumar%20government%20had%20launched%20a%20caste%20census%20in%20Bihar%20in%20January%20this%20year%2C%20and%20said%20that%20detailed%20information%20on%20socio-economic%20conditions%20would%20help%20create%20better%20government%20policy%20to%20aid%20disadvantaged%20groups.%20The%20entire%20exercise%20was%20supposed%20to%20have%20been%20completed%20by%20May.%20However%2C%20the%20legal%20challenges%20meant%20the%20government%20was%20unable%20to%20complete%20the%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20May%204%2C%20the%20Patna%20high%20court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fpatna-high-court-puts-interim-stay-on-bihars-caste-census%5C%22%3Eput%20a%20stay%20on%20the%20caste%20census%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CPrima%20facie%2C%20we%20are%20of%20the%20opinion%20that%20the%20State%20has%20no%20power%20to%20carry%20out%20a%20caste-based%20survey%2C%20in%20the%20manner%20in%20which%20it%20is%20fashioned%20now%2C%20which%20would%20amount%20to%20a%20census%2C%20thus%20impinging%20upon%20the%20legislative%20power%20of%20the%20Union%20Parliament.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20May%2018%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-refuses-to-lift-patna-hcs-stay-on-bihar-caste-census%5C%22%3Erefused%20to%20lift%20the%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20stay%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20caste%20census%20has%20become%20a%20major%20political%20concern%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20with%20opposition%20parties%20amping%20up%20the%20pressure%20on%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20do%20the%20exercise%20on%20a%20national%20basis.%20It%20was%20the%20Congress-led%20UPA%20government%20which%20first%20conducted%20a%20Socio-Economic%20and%20Caste%20Census%20(SECC)%20in%202011-12%20but%20never%20released%20its%20data%20because%20of%20varied%20opinions%20about%20it%20within%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-caste-census-ideological-unity-opposition%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0has%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20was%20more%20vocally%20expressed%20by%20different%20opposition%20parties%20after%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20implemented%20reservation%20for%20the%20Economically%20Weaker%20Classes%20(EWS)%2C%20which%20effectively%20gave%20a%20quota%20to%20the%20so-called%20%E2%80%9Cupper%20caste%E2%80%9D%20groups.%20The%20EWS%20reservation%20was%20seen%20as%20an%20anomaly%20in%20the%20caste-based%20affirmative%20action%20policy%20because%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fews-quota-a-stupefying-inversion-of-the-idea-of-equality%5C%22%3Ethe%20criteria%20was%20poverty%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20was%20perceived%20by%20various%20parties%20as%20a%20move%20to%20deny%20marginalised%20castes%20and%20communities%20their%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690878923000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F12%2F06201106%2FPatna_high_court1.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fpatna-high-court-dismisses-petitions-against-bihar-caste-census%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20bench%20of%20Chief%20Justice%20K.%C2%A0Vinod%20Chandran%20and%20Justice%20Partha%20Sarthy%20delivered%20its%20on%20five%20petitions%20challenging%20the%20survey.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fpatna-high-court-dismisses-petitions-against-bihar-caste-census%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Patna%20HC%20holds%20caste%20survey%20in%20Bihar%20as%20valid%20and%20legal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2