2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20travelled%20to%20these%20%E2%80%9Cborder%E2%80%9D%20areas%20within%20the%20state%20of%20Manipur%2C%20after%20curfew%20hours%2C%20to%20witness%20what%20happens%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EBy%209%20pm%2C%20Imphal%E2%80%99s%20streets%20are%20entirely%20deserted%20except%20for%20Meira%20Paibis%2C%20who%20roam%20them%20as%20vigilants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThis%20reporter%20and%20a%20trusted%20driver%20begin%20a%20journey%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Cborder%E2%80%9D%20of%20Bishnupur%20district.%20From%20Imphal%20to%20Bishnupur%2C%20our%20car%20is%20halted%20twice%20by%20Mera%20Paibis%2C%20and%20once%20by%20local%20men.%20The%20latter%20inspect%20the%20vehicle%20thoroughly%2C%20including%20its%20boot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EClose%20to%20Bishnupur%2C%20some%20locals%20who%20appeared%20intoxicated%20once%20again%20stopped%20our%20car.%20This%20group%20appeared%20to%20be%20diligently%20checking%20every%20vehicle%20passing%20through%20the%20Kuki-dominated%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ETreatment%20towards%20vehicles%20differ%20depending%20on%20whether%20you%20are%20traveling%20to%20or%20from%20the%20hills.%20Meiteis%20in%20the%20valley%20inspect%20cars%20coming%20from%20the%20hills%C2%A0while%20Kukis%20scrutinise%20vehicles%20headed%20towards%20the%20hills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAs%20we%20approached%20the%20area%20of%20Terakhongshangbi%2C%20our%20car%20was%20stopped%20by%20a%20few%20locals%20who%20urgently%20requested%20that%20we%20turn%20off%20our%20lights%20as%20firing%20was%20taking%20place%20in%20the%20vicinity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAround%2020%20women%20were%20sitting%20in%20a%20small%20cottage.%20They%20told%20The%20Wire%20that%20they%20were%20Meira%20Paibis.%20One%20woman%20who%20identified%20her%20as%20Sanahanbi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20government%20started%20ruling%20the%20state%2C%20we%20thought%20that%20all%20our%20miseries%20and%20grievances%20would%20be%20heard.%20But%20this%20didn%E2%80%99t%20happen.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESanahanbi%20said%20that%20she%20would%20still%20appeal%20to%20Biren%20to%20solve%20the%20present%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAs%20the%20sound%20of%20guns%20continued%2C%20the%20Meira%20Paibis%20in%20the%20cottage%20turned%20off%20the%20lights.%20Another%20woman%2C%20who%20identified%20herself%20as%20Sanatombi%2C%20questioned%20the%20government%20for%20still%20banning%20a%20significant%20portion%20of%20internet%20services.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20the%20Meitei%20people%20were%20given%20access%20to%20internet%2C%20more%20stories%20of%20suffering%20would%20come%20to%20be%20known.%20A%20month%20ago%2C%20police%20promised%20to%20provide%20protection%20to%20farmers%20and%20encouraged%20them%20to%20start%20farming.%20Those%20who%20went%20to%20reap%20rice%20were%20captured%20by%20Kuki%20militants%20and%20have%20been%20missing%20since%20then%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ESanatombi%20also%20expressed%20her%20disappointment%20in%20the%20governments%20at%20the%20state%20and%20Union%2C%20stating%2C%20%E2%80%9CAmit%20Shah%20came%20to%20%3Cspan%3EManipur%3C%2Fspan%3E%20but%20failed%20to%20hear%20our%20grievances.%20Many%20times%2C%20we%E2%80%99ve%20expressed%20our%20woes%20to%20everyone%2C%20including%20the%20media%2C%20but%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20receive%20any%20help.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20the%20Meitei%20speaking%20group%2C%20there%20was%20a%20woman%20who%20spoke%20in%20Hindi.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20weapons%2C%20but%20we%20are%20still%20ready%20to%20fight%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EA%20bullet%20whizzed%20past.%20We%20trooped%20outside%20and%20the%20women%20sa