earmarked%20for%20a%20mosque%20on%20August%2011%2C%202006%20and%20having%20secured%20a%20clearance%20for%20its%20building%20plans%20earlier%2C%20further%20construction%20has%20not%20recommenced%20pending%20revalidation%20of%20the%20plans%20from%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESupreme%20Court%20dismissed%20petition%20against%20it%20this%20May%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20only%20recently%2C%20on%20May%201%2C%20that%20a%20two-judge%20bench%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20finally%20dismissed%20the%20petition%20against%20the%20mosque.%20The%20court%20said%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20hearing%20the%20learned%20counsel%20for%20the%20parties%2C%20we%20are%20not%20convinced%20that%20the%20petitioners%20have%20made%20out%20a%20case%20for%20exercising%20jurisdiction%20under%20Article%20136%20of%20the%20Constitution.%20However%2C%20we%20reiterate%20the%20observations%20and%20directions%20which%20are%20contained%20in%20the%20impugned%20order(s)%20which%20shall%20be%20strictly%20complied%20with%20by%20the%20sixth%20respondent-%20Haryana%20Anjuman%20Charitable%20Trust%20as%20also%20the%20Public%20Authority.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20record%20the%20submission%20of%20learned%20counsel%20for%20the%20sixth%20respondent%20that%20the%20sixth%20respondent%20will%20make%20available%20volunteers%20(Traffic%20Volunteers)%20so%20that%20the%20problem%20arising%20out%20of%20increasing%20traffic%20is%20adequately%20redressed.%20That%20apart%2C%20we%20direct%20that%20over%20and%20above%20the%20said%20assurance%20being%20recorded%2C%20that%20the%20Commissioner%20of%20Traffic%20Police%2C%20Gurugram%2C%20Haryana%20will%20deploy%20police%20personnel%20in%20sufficient%20numbers%20as%20and%20when%20required%20and%20particularly%20without%20fail%20on%20every%20Friday%20so%20that%20they%20will%20efficiently%20control%20and%20regulate%20the%20Traffic%20in%20such%20a%20way%20that%20all%20the%20people%20in%20the%20area%20are%20least%20inconvenienced.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EWe%20further%20record%20the%20submission%20of%20the%20learned%20counsel%20for%20the%20sixth%20respondent%20that%20there%20will%20be%20no%20noise%20pollution%20caused%20by%20it%20and%20the%20sixth%20respondent%20shall%20not%20use%20loud%20speakers%20for%20Azaan.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Commissioner%20of%20Traffic%20Police%2C%20Gurugram%2C%20Haryana%20will%20make%20assessment%20and%20make%20suitable%20arrangements%20so%20that%20apart%20from%20Fridays%2C%20police%20personnel%20are%20always%20present%20so%20as%20to%20obviate%20any%20untoward%20situation.%20He%20may%20consider%20establishing%20a%20Traffic%20Police%20Post%2FBooth%20in%20the%20vicinity%20of%20the%20Mosque%20in%20question%2C%20if%20he%20deems%20it%20fit.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESubject%20to%20the%20aforesaid%20directions%2C%20the%20special%20leave%20petitions%20are%20disposed%20of.%20Pending%20application(s)%2C%20if%20any%2C%20stand%20disposed%20of.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20context%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20learnt%20that%20a%20few%20weeks%20before%20this%20attack%2C%20the%20mosque%20had%20been%20attacked%20by%20miscreants%20from%20a%20neighbouring%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20had%20acted%20promptly%20on%20information%20being%20shared%20with%20them%20and%20detained%20several%20attackers.%20However%2C%20due%20to%20intervention%20of%20residents%20and%20elders%2C%20in%20order%20to%20restore%20peace%20in%20the%20area%2C%20the%20matter%20was%20ultimately%20resolved%20by%20negotiation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20six%20months%20after%20the%20construction%20on%20the%20plot%20allotted%20for%20the%20mosque%20began%20in%202004%2C%20some%20real%20estate%20agents%20etc.%20moved%20the%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20high%20court%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20land%20allocated%20for%20the%20mosque%20was%20earmarked%20for%20other%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20was%20rejected%20by%20the%20high%20court%20but%20an%20order%20was%20obtained%20to%20%E2%80%9Cmaintain%20status-quo%E2%80%9D%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20lasted%20for%2012%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20despite%20being%20granted%20permission%20from%20the%20authorities%20to%20build%20three%20storeys%2C%20only%20the%20basement%20and%20the%20ground%20floor%20were%20built%20where%20prayers%20were%20held.%20The%20namaz%20controversy%20in%20Gurugram%20had%20driven%20more%20and%20more%20Muslims%20to%20pray%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20building%20plan%20of%20the%20mosque%20has%20been%20sanctioned%20by%20the%20government%2C%20it%20is%20possible%20to%20do%20the%20work%20only%20if%20construction%20starts%20within%20a%20stipulated%20time%20period%20of%20getting%20the%20permission.%20As%20the%20stay%20meant%20that%20time%20was%20missed%2C%20sources%20say%20that%20%E2%80%9Cpermission%20to%20revalidate%20the%20old%20building%20plan%20is%20pending%20in%20the%20chief%20minister%2C%20M.L.%20Khattar%E2%80%99s%20office%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690868375000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F01110555%2FScreenshot-2023-08-01-at-10.53.01-AM_cleanup.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fgurugram-mosque-set-on-fire-was-the-only-one-of-govt-allocated-land-in-the-area%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20mosque%20had%20been%20under%20constant%20attack%20and%20the%20last%20one%20was%20just%20a%20few%20weeks%20ago.%20The%20difference%20this%20time%20was%20the%20intensity%20of%20the%20attack%20and%20the%20stabbing%20of%20the%20deputy%20imam%2C%20who%20succumbed%20to%20the%20assault.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A36%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fgurugram-mosque-set-on-fire-was-the-only-one-of-govt-allocated-land-in-the-area%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22t