%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20unique%20wearable%20for%20high-risk%20mothers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenthil%20also%20created%20a%20smart%20wearable%20device%20called%20Allowear%2C%20designed%20for%20high-risk%20pregnant%20women%20who%20need%20continuous%20monitoring.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20says%20that%20this%20battery-operated%20device%20tracks%20their%20sleep%20cycle%2C%20calories%20burned%20(indicating%20nutritional%20deficiencies)%2C%20pulse%20rate%2C%20and%20steps.%20It%20also%20sends%20timely%20reminders%20for%20taking%20medicines.%20ASHA%20(Accredited%20Social%20Health%20Activist)%20workers%20can%20retrieve%20the%20recorded%20health%20data%20through%20Bluetooth%20and%20upload%20it%20to%20the%20cloud%2C%20where%20doctors%20can%20access%20it%20for%20review%2C%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenthil%20explains%20a%20scenario%20where%20such%20devices%20are%20useful.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20high-risk%20mother%20has%20high%20blood%20pressure%2C%20doctors%20also%20consider%20her%20sleep%20pattern.%20If%20she%20isn%E2%80%99t%20getting%20proper%20sleep%2C%20it%20can%20contribute%20to%20increased%20blood%20pressure.%20In%20such%20cases%2C%20the%20doctor%20may%20prescribe%20different%20medications%20instead%20of%20a%20standard%20blood%20pressure%20tablet.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20is%20collected%20weekly%20and%20reviewed%20by%20a%20doctor%20every%2015%20days.%20High-risk%20mothers%20are%20recommended%20to%20use%20the%20wearable%20device%20for%201%2C000%20days%20%E2%80%94%20starting%20from%20the%20fourth%20week%20of%20pregnancy%20until%20the%20baby%E2%80%99s%20second%20birthday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-1690549999.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Senthil%20also%20created%20a%20smart%20wearable%20device%20called%20Allowear%2C%20designed%20for%20high-risk%20pregnant%20women%20who%20need%20continuous%20monitoring.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-1690549999.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-1690549999-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-1690549999-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-1690549999-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fjiovio-1690549999-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-325671%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESenthil%20also%20created%20a%20smart%20wearable%20device%20called%20Allowear%2C%20designed%20for%20high-risk%20pregnant%20women%20who%20need%20continuous%20monitoring.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20cost%20for%20this%20service%20is%20only%20Re%201%20per%20day%2C%20covered%20by%20the%20government.%20Senthil%20says%20that%20their%20annual%20revenue%20is%20about%20Rs%201.5%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommenting%20on%20how%20useful%20the%20devices%20are%2C%20Madurai-based%20Dr%20S%20Karthikeyan%2C%20who%20has%20been%20practising%20medicine%20for%2013%20years%2C%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20seen%20that%20a%20lot%20of%20pregnant%20women%20do%20not%20take%20care%20of%20themselves%20which%20causes%20nutritional%20deficiencies%20among%20them.%20This%20changes%20their%20blood%20glucose%20and%20pressure%2C%20and%20ECG.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20these%20devices%2C%20we%20are%20able%20to%20understand%20the%20problems%20and%20alert%20local%20healthcare%20workers.%20Accordingly%2C%20we%20are%20also%20able%20to%20prescribe%20iron%20supplements%2C%20folic%20acid%20ta